article_id:2673,category_name:News,title_name:Part One of Chapter 23: The Progenitor Added to the Main Campaign!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ffb3dd5ac61735094989a950396fd2e9.png,message:<div>Part one of Chapter 23: The Progenitor was added to the main campaign on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1639980000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ffb3dd5ac61735094989a950396fd2e9.png"></div><div><br></div><div>The Holy City of Grams has been devastated by Satan, and as if mocking those working toward its reconstruction, the Progenitor&#39;s shadow yet looms above. It seems the return of the creator is nigh thanks to the dark machinations of the two princes Phares and Beren.</div><div><br></div><div>We hope you&#39;re looking forward to seeing what&#39;s in store for the prince and his friends!</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Part one of chapter 23 of the main campaign will unlock when you clear Ch. 22 / 5-4 &quot;What&#39;s Left Behind.&quot;</div><div>2. The release of part one does not include additional dragons who can be unbound using draconic essences, but you can use the draconic essence icon displayed on the area map for each chapter in the main campaign to check the dragon whose draconic essence you can obtain, how many draconic essences you currently have, how many more you can obtain, and the quests from which you can obtain draconic essences.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1639980000,update_time1639963385